article.headline: Lehigh 80, Muhlenberg 70
article.story: BETHLEHEM, Pa. (AP) -- Jose Olivero scored 25 points to lead Lehigh to an 80-70 victory over Muhlenberg on Wednesday. Olivero is now just 15 points shy of 1,000 for his career. He also led the game in assists with 8. Mike Fischman scored 13 points for Lehigh (7-8) and junior Jason Mgebroff added 10. Jeff Stewart scored 28 points and had 13 rebounds, both game highs, for Muhlenberg (5-5). He was 7-for-8 in free throws. Chris Huber added 20 points for the Mules. Lehigh led 37-24 at halftime.
